onnect to sewage treatment plants.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/sambhajinagar-to-enforce-higher-property-tax-on-drain-top-buildings-amid-sewage-crackdown/131290128?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-680157/131290128.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}